        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Complete Macro Breakdown</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Get precise macronutrients, protein, carbs, and fats for the entire recipe and per serving.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-lemon-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lemon-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Instant Results</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          No manual ingredient lookup or tedious calculations. Get comprehensive nutrition data in seconds.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 